  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Secondary progressive MS in an active stage

          -  EDSS between 3 and 6

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Benign or primary progressive MS

          -  Patients with cardiac risk factors

          -  Patients who have already received mitoxantrone
      </textblock>
